14#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_RKEY_57_C
15#define RDATA_GENERIC_RKEY_57_C
16
17#define RRTYPE_RKEY_ATTRIBUTES 0
18
19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_rkey(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21
22 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
23
24 return (generic_fromtext_key(rdclass, type, lexer, origin,
25 options, target, callbacks));
26}
27
28static inline isc_result_t
29totext_rkey(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
30
31 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
32 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
33
34 return (generic_totext_key(rdata, tctx, target));
35}
36
37static inline isc_result_t
38fromwire_rkey(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
39
40 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
41
42 return (generic_fromwire_key(rdclass, type, source, dctx,
43 options, target));
44}
45
46static inline isc_result_t
47towire_rkey(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
48 isc_region_t sr;
49
50 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
51 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
52 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
53
54 UNUSED(cctx);
55
56 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
57 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
58}
59
60static inline int
61compare_rkey(ARGS_COMPARE) {
62 isc_region_t r1;
63 isc_region_t r2;
64
65 REQUIRE(rdata1 != NULL);
66 REQUIRE(rdata2 != NULL);
67 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
68 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
69 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
70 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
71 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
72
73 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
74 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
75 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
76}
77
78static inline isc_result_t
79fromstruct_rkey(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
80
81 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
82
83 return (generic_fromstruct_key(rdclass, type, source, target));
84}
85
86static inline isc_result_t
87tostruct_rkey(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
88 dns_rdata_rkey_t *rkey = target;
89
90 REQUIRE(rkey != NULL);
91 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
92 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
93
94 rkey->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
95 rkey->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
96 ISC_LINK_INIT(&rkey->common, link);
97
98 return (generic_tostruct_key(rdata, target, mctx));
99}
100
101static inline void
102freestruct_rkey(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
103 dns_rdata_rkey_t *rkey = (dns_rdata_rkey_t *) source;
104
105 REQUIRE(rkey != NULL);
106 REQUIRE(rkey->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
107
108 generic_freestruct_key(source);
109}
110
111static inline isc_result_t
112additionaldata_rkey(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
113
114 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
115
116 UNUSED(rdata);
117 UNUSED(add);
118 UNUSED(arg);
119
120 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
121}
122
123static inline isc_result_t
124digest_rkey(ARGS_DIGEST) {
125 isc_region_t r;
126
127 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
128 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
129
130 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
131
132 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
133}
134
135static inline bool
136checkowner_rkey(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
137
138 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
139
140 UNUSED(name);
141 UNUSED(type);
142 UNUSED(rdclass);
143 UNUSED(wildcard);
144
145 return (true);
146}
147
148static inline bool
149checknames_rkey(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
150
151 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
152 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rkey);
153
154 UNUSED(rdata);
155 UNUSED(owner);
156 UNUSED(bad);
157
158 return (true);
159}
160
161static inline int
162casecompare_rkey(ARGS_COMPARE) {
163
164 /*
165 * Treat ALG 253 (private DNS) subtype name case sensistively.
166 */
167 return (compare_rkey(rdata1, rdata2));
168}
